{{version030}}
{{flavour|You are unnaturally agile, and gain a bonus to your evasion.}}

'''Agility''' is a [[status effect]] that provides +5 [[evasion]].

The [[demonspawn]] mutation, [[Powered by Pain]] may provide the Agility status effect. It can also result as a [[chaos]] effect.

==History==
*In [[0.25]], [[potions of agility]], the most common source of this status, were replaced by [[potions of stabbing]]. In addition, its +50 [[stealth]] and +5 [[dexterity]] boosts were removed, and Agility is now a valid chaos effect.
